Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew reached Fishman Island located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates who are looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after Shirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:04:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 30,000 human slaves we've caught in the sea over the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And 70,000 Fishmen who know how to use arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They moved here from the closed Fishman District.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...100,000 outlaws altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how powerful I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power that I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I started this whole thing 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Concerning the late Queen of the Ryugu Kingdom, who you fools still love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Otohime was killed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother was not murdered by a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I, her kinsman, did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I, standing in front of you now, killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:44.09,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Shirahoshi's Tears! Luffy Finally Shows Up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you already knew that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...I killed your mother, Shirahoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A few years after it happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Megalo told me secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Megalo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Megalo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Megalo was owned by Neptune's army back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And he witnessed everything that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi, why didn't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I told anyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone would hold a grudge against Hody-sama, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is not what Mother-sama wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last promise we made with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She told us that no matter who did it to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we should not get angry or hate anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't matter who did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get angry on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let resentment or hatred get the better of you for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You did as Mother said to do 10 years ago and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:09:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...you have been keeping this to yourself all this time, alone in Hard Shell Tower?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She tried not to harbor hate for the one who killed her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it was her dying mother's wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it's almost unthinkable someone would be able to keep such a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She is such an obedient, admirable girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else could have done such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it! Hey, Megalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had cried out right there, you could've drawn everybody's attention
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and let them know that I was the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you for shutting your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you for confiding only in this dumb girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were anybody else, we couldn't have come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Shirahoshi, what you did was pretty stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we call those actions in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you tried to stymie your hate for me, this kingdom will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,your father, your brothers, the citizens, and you yourself are all going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't listen to him, Princess-sama! You did nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was definitely foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,King! Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Father-sama! Brothers-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how miserable they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We are doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Great warriors?! Pathetic! They're barely alive now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because Captain Hody is so strong-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't make it until the time of execution-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good. They must be executed by beheading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only concern was Jinbe and Shirahoshi, and we got them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no reason for us to wait until the appointed time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to execute these worthless creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They deserve death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No! They're really gonna kill Neptune the Great Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hell on earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They have 100,000 outlaws on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it for our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Sharley!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Children...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me! When will the pirate with a hat come to destroy the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me! When will it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. All I know is what will happen in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be tomorrow or a year from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to come now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If they create havoc here now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we might be in trouble but those villains would be too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to come now, too! I don't want them to kill the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better if they came now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to destroy the island, why don't you do it now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your worst - right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Can you hear us, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're hiding somewhere on the island, come here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic! They're literally clutching at straws!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharley's previsions were always accurate but this time, it's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How meaningless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those fools must be out of their minds. Let's bring them to their senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you stupid citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:16:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to proceed with the execution of the former king, Neptune - now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch very closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As I cut former king Neptune's head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this half-assed king without a drop of racial pride will be gone forever
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the new kingdom of Fishmen will rise, which will dominate the pathetic humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put an end to the shameless Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How regrettable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Megalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He really showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you see that? He saved King Neptune.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And right before that, Princess Shirahoshi cried for his help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he come out of the shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he hiding in its stomach?! But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're out already... But I guess you had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Much! What the... Who is he talking to-ch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! We were ready from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we knew that Luffy would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...sit tight as we had planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirage, release!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman appeared all of a sudden-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it, Jinbe-chan? The letter from the Celestial Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Whoa! The letter is gone! When did she take it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I handed the key over to Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The key's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look up! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A whale and a lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaon Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is your chance! Go, Whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Princes! Take the King and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do that! Wait-zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it took the King and the Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Give us back the royal family-gaban!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Jinbe hatched a plan with the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that he really came.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look how many people there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, are they all our enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so. It looks like there are 70,000 or 80,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, 100,000 of them, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go take a nap or something if you want. I'll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go wild, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the members of the Straw Hats are coming out of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to destroy the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you occupy the Ryugu Palace?! Do you want to kill the royal family too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you guys who kidnapped the Mermaids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you people friends or foes to Fishman Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:23:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends or foes? That's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll have to decide on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats have gathered in the Conchcorde Plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hody proclaims that he will become Pirate King,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and sends the vast force of the New Fishman Pirates to attack Luffy's crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten pirates will battle to decide the fate of Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.03,0:23:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Big Clash! The Straw Hats vs. A Hundred Thousand Enemies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
